    public class Invitation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Java class defining and incapacitating the characteristics of an Invitation between users of the system; The Invitation is used in asking fo permission to add a certain user as participant in a specific Party When an invitation is answered it is used as a notification
